.DS_Store
# Compiled C shim — platform-specific, built on install from helpers-mcp.c
helpers-mcp
# Native MCP tools — platform-specific, built on install from native/ (Rust).
# Rust-only: no Node fallback. The committed source is the native/ crate.
/helpers-native
# The `helpers` CLI is a busybox symlink to helpers-native, recreated by
# `helpers build`/install (was previously the tracked Node CLI, now removed).
/helpers
native/target/
# Ported git-* CLIs — symlinks to helpers-native, recreated by `helpers build`.
# The committed source is native/src/gitcli/. Keep in sync with GITCLI_NAMES.
/git-resolve
/git-remerge
/git-fucked-the-push
/git-initialize
/git-get
/git-scan-for-leaked-envs
/git-upload
/git-checkpoint
/git-help-i-pushed-an-env
# Generated project index (cheap repo map) — rebuilt on demand by `helpers index`.
# Match at any depth: sub-crates (e.g. native/.helpers/) get their own index cache.
**/.helpers/index/
# Generated build-out plan from `helpers setup` (regenerable; not source).
**/.helpers/SETUP.md
*.dxbundle
build/
coverage/
dist/
vscode-extension/*.vsix
vision-tool/*.vsix
vscode-extension/node_modules/
vision-tool/node_modules/
.vscode/aioserver-vision-ipc.json
.vscode/helpers-vision-ipc.json
.github/session-memory/*
!.github/session-memory/.gitkeep
.env
atlas-api/.env*-chat-history.jsonl

# Local release credentials (never committed) — fill + run scripts/setup-github-release-config.sh
*.local.env

# Crawler output — regenerated by scripts/crawl-docs.mjs (can be large/deep)
crawl-index/

# Packed lint-module store — trained artifacts the ModuleRegistry republishes on demand
# (in a real deployment this points at a shared module repo, not the source tree).
lint-modules/

# Lint rule catalogs — fetched from official docs at training time; not committed.
# Only sources.json (URL registry) and SCHEMA.md (schema doc) are committed.
lint-index/*.json
!lint-index/sources.json
